        <button id="book-now-button" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('booking', vehicle_id=vehicle.vehicle_id) }}'">Book Now</button>
        <div id="vehicle-reviews">
            <h2>Customer Reviews</h2>
            <ul>
                {% for review in reviews %}
                <li><strong>{{ review.user }}:</strong> {{ review.comment }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </div>
        <button onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('search_vehicles') }}'">Back to Search</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

templates/booking.html
```html
'''
Booking page template for CarRental.
Allows user to select pickup/dropoff locations and dates, calculate price.
'''
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Book Your Rental</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="booking-page">
        <h1>Book Your Rental - {{ vehicle.make }} {{ vehicle.model }}</h1>
        <form method="post">
            <label for="pickup-location">Pickup Location:</label>
            <select id="pickup-location" name="pickup_location" required>
                {% for loc in locations %}
                <option value="{{ loc.city }}" {% if pickup_location == loc.city %}selected{% endif %}>{{ loc.city }}</option>
                {% endfor %}
            </select><br>

            <label for="dropoff-location">Dropoff Location:</label>
            <select id="dropoff-location" name="dropoff_location" required>
                {% for loc in locations %}
                <option value="{{ loc.city }}" {% if dropoff_location == loc.city %}selected{% endif %}>{{ loc.city }}</option>
                {% endfor %}
            </select><br>

            <label for="pickup-date">Pickup Date:</label>
            <input type="date" id="pickup-date" name="pickup_date" value="{{ pickup_date }}" required><br>

            <label for="dropoff-date">Dropoff Date:</label>
            <input type="date" id="dropoff-date" name="dropoff_date" value="{{ dropoff_date }}" required><br>

            <button id="calculate-price-button" type="submit">Calculate Price</button>
        </form>
        <div id="total-price">
            {% if total_price is not none %}
            <p>Total Price: ${{ '%.2f'|format(total_price) }}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if total_price and total_price > 0 %}
        <button id="proceed-to-insurance-button" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('insurance_options') }}'">Proceed to Insurance Options</button>
        {% endif %}
        <button onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('vehicle_details', vehicle_id=vehicle.vehicle_id) }}'">Back to Vehicle Details</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

templates/insurance_options.html
```html
'''
Insurance Options page template for CarRental.
Displays insurance plans and allows selection and confirmation.
'''
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Select Insurance Coverage</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="insurance-page">
        <h1>Select Insurance Coverage</h1>
        <form method="post">
            <div id="insurance-options">
                {% for plan in insurance_plans %}
                <div>
                    <input type="radio" id="select-insurance-{{ plan.insurance_id }}" name="insurance_plan" value="{{ plan.insurance_id }}"
                    {% if selected_plan and selected_plan.insurance_id == plan.insurance_id %}checked{% endif %} required>
                    <label for="select-insurance-{{ plan.insurance_id }}">{{ plan.plan_name }} - ${{ '%.2f'|format(plan.daily_cost) }} per day</label>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
            <div id="insurance-description">
                {% if selected_plan %}
                <p>{{ selected_plan.description }}</p>
                {% else %}
                <p>Please select an insurance plan to see details.</p>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div id="insurance-price">
                {% if selected_plan %}
                <p>Price: ${{ '%.2f'|format(selected_plan.daily_cost) }} per day</p>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <button id="confirm-booking-button" type="submit">Confirm Booking</button>
        </form>
        {% if confirmed %}
        <p>Booking confirmed with selected insurance plan.</p>
        {% endif %}
        <button onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('booking', vehicle_id=1) }}'">Back to Booking</button>
        <button onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('dashboard') }}'">Back to Dashboard</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

templates/rental_history.html
```html
'''
Rental History page template for CarRental.
Displays previous rentals with status filter and navigation.
'''
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Rental History</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="history-page">
        <h1>Rental History</h1>
        <form method="get" action="{{ url_for('rental_history') }}">
            <label for="status-filter">Filter by Status:</label>
            <select id="status-filter" name="status" onchange="this.form.submit()">
                <option value="All" {% if status_filter == 'All' %}selected{% endif %}>All</option>
                <option value="Active" {% if status_filter == 'Active' %}selected{% endif %}>Active</option>
                <option value="Completed" {% if status_filter == 'Completed' %}selected{% endif %}>Completed</option>
                <option value="Cancelled" {% if status_filter == 'Cancelled' %}selected{% endif %}>Cancelled</option>
            </select>
        </form>
        <table id="rentals-table" border="1">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>ID</th>
                    <th>Vehicle ID</th>
                    <th>Pickup Date</th>
                    <th>Dropoff Date</th>
                    <th>Pickup Location</th>
                    <th>Dropoff Location</th>
                    <th>Total Price</th>
                    <th>Status</th>
                    <th>Details</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for rental in rentals %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ rental.rental_id }}</td>
                    <td>{{ rental.vehicle_id }}</td>
                    <td>{{ rental.pickup_date }}</td>
                    <td>{{ rental.dropoff_date }}</td>
                    <td>{{ rental.pickup_location }}</td>
                    <td>{{ rental.dropoff_location }}</td>
                    <td>${{ rental.total_price }}</td>
                    <td>{{ rental.status }}</td>
                    <td><button id="view-rental-details-{{ rental.rental_id }}" onclick="alert('Rental details for ID {{ rental.rental_id }}')">View Details</button></td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <button id="back-to-dashboard" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('dashboard') }}'">Back to Dashboard</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

